NETHERLANDS COASTGUARD
NAVIGATIONAL WARNING - ADDITIONAL NR. 26 291803 UTC DEC
WARNING SEASTATE
WAVE HEIGHT WARNING 300CM TSS TERSCHELLING - GERMAN BIGHT
ISSUED AT 291800 UTC DEC
CONTAINER VESSELS WITH A LENGTH OF 100-200M ARE AT
RISK OF LOSING CONTAINERS DURING HEAVY SEA CONDITIONS
IN PARTICULAR FROM A WEST-NORTHWEST TO
NORTHERLY DIRECTION. THESE VESSELS SHOULD ALTER
COURSE IF NECESSARY TO AVOID COMING ABEAM TO THE
WAVES AND TAKE OTHER APPROPRIATE MEASURES TO AVOID
LOSING CONTAINERS.
